Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.25,0:00:16.57,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.15,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not budging at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:21.79,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, that was some decent force.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:24.03,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Is this guy for real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:27.31,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,He could give Nanami-san a run for \Nhis money in terms of physical blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:29.54,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Though I suppose that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:32.26,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rather sturdy veil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:34.53,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to search for its weak point
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:37.05,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,and put a hole in it, \Neven if it's only for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:39.85,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get anywhere \Nwithout getting inside first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.67,0:00:42.55,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:44.35,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:47.86,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, this is a veil to keep sorcerers out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:50.19,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,It's a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:53.91,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Barriers are all designed to surround\Nyou and protect yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:57.36,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Which fundamentally means \Nthat whoever lowered this veil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:01:00.08,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,is inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:03.99,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,But back in Harajuku...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:09.79,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:13.58,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,So staying outside the veil instead of \Nsurrounding themselves with it increases
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:15.79,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,the risk of being discovered and defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:17.79,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,thereby raising the strength of the veil.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:20.69,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real egg of Columbus idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:22.02,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:26.02,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Though, man, they're completely ignoring \Nthe fundamentals of barriers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:27.82,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,What a crazy idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:32.88,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can see why the barrier didn't \Nbreak from Yuji's earlier blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:34.37,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the logic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:38.09,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,the veil's source should be somewhere \Nthat really stands out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:40.95,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,By increasing the risk of discovery,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:43.43,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,they're further increasing \Nits strength, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:47.83,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere that stands out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:52.96,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fnArial\bord0\shad0\b1\pos(320,300)}22:01 Shibuya Central Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.80,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Think the sorcerers will realize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:07.55,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,This is the place that stands out \Nthe most within the veil, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:09.29,Main,Ogami,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:12.14,Main,Grandson,0000,0000,0000,,But even if they do realize it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.62,0:02:13.89,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:18.69,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,The lower floors are swarming \Nwith those transfigured humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.88,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,They won't be able to \Nclimb up here that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:28.95,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wires?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:30.60,Main,Maki,0000,0000,0000,,These are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:31.48,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,0)\pos(92,36)\fs18\bord1\shad0\c&H716DA4&\3c&HF3E5EE&}These are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:43.93,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Do these bastards know \Nabout the entrusted veil?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:47.39,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Just as planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:50.52,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the source of the veil?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.61,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. According to Mei-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:55.62,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,it already has the barrier programmed in,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:59.48,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,and it just needs someone \Nto pour cursed energy into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:02.61,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Which means as long as we destroy those,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:05.49,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,we can ignore the curse users until later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:08.83,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,There were three of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:12.08,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,The veil keeping sorcerers \Nout is still active.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:13.82,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the remaining two?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.01,0:03:16.21,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,With him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:34.11,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Fushiguro! Dismiss Nue!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:43.19,Main,Ogami,0000,0000,0000,,Grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:47.11,Main,Grandson,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:50.56,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,I have some endearing underclassmen now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.56,0:03:54.29,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,so it's time to earn some achievements here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:58.28,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,so I can become a first-grade, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:03.39,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Fushiguro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:05.75,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:07.13,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:11.46,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see the moment of impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:14.50,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,His body is too clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:17.31,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he is a sorcerer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:20.31,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,he plummeted from the 41st floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:23.31,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Get up, you old trickster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.04,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:37.51,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Youngsters these days have \Nno pity for the elderly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:39.91,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,We can't waste time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:41.61,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:45.00,Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 35\N{\fs30\fscy150}Seance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:05:00.07,Show_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,825)\pos(320,10)\3c&H8ECEDD&}JUJUTSU KAISEN\N{\fs16\bord0\fscy100\c&HDEDCE0&}Shibuya Incident
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:21.27,Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so insistent \Non my recommendation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:25.78,Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You could easily become \Nsemi-first-grade with your technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:30.05,Flashback,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Because I believe it's important \Nto do things the right way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:34.03,Flashback,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Especially with bloody \Nwork like being a sorcerer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:39.54,Flashback,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not that bright, so sometimes \NI don't know what the right way is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:43.90,Flashback,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,So whenever I'm at a loss, I think to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:47.36,Flashback,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,"What would Nanami-san do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:52.25,Flashback,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,So it wouldn't be right to become \Na first-grade without your approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:55.77,Flashback,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, would you like another drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:57.76,Flashback,Nanamni,0000,0000,0000,,A makgeolli.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.23,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Auspicious Beast Summon: #1,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:04.24,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Kaichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:14.12,Italics,Grandson,0000,0000,0000,,It's homing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:17.75,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The Seance technique, \NAuspicious Beast Summon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.78,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,By hiding his face, Ino can \Nbecome a spiritual medium
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:23.99,Narration,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,used to manifest the powers \Nof the four auspicious beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:27.19,Main,Grandson,0000,0000,0000,,Granny, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:30.00,Main,Ogami,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, quite the coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:34.51,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Number 2, Reiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:37.23,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san entrusted those two to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:39.26,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't just leave them alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:43.26,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,but it would be a bad idea to \Nlead these two to them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:47.02,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,The best option is to kill them fast \Nand rejoin my underclassmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:13.52,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Adapt to the facts, \Nand maintain self-control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:17.27,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Cast aside pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:33.17,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, matching pace with him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:36.65,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,takes more effort than matching the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:03.98,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Itadori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.73,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,All good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.05,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a scratch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.24,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,So full of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:12.99,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,What promising futures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.44,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Makes it worth killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:21.46,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Dog's claws can \Nhurt even special-grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.32,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,I hit him with serious force, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:27.25,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Then how...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:30.97,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,is he not damaged at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:34.03,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this wouldn't take long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:35.71,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,No comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.71,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\frz282.5\pos(76.666,183.333)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H1D1618&\3c&HF4F8FA&\bord1}No comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:54.86,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,He's just as he seems—not all that strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:59.61,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,But he's doing whatever it takes and \Nsacrificing himself to protect that old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:03.11,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,There's something more to them.\NI should hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.63,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Their aura's changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:13.54,Main,Ogami,0000,0000,0000,,We're all set now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:15.63,Main,Grandson,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:16.87,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:28.02,Main,Ogami,0000,0000,0000,,Zen'in Toji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:36.62,Main,Ogami,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:42.03,Main,Grandson,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's great, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.35,Main,Grandson,0000,0000,0000,,Better than any before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:51.09,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\1c&H75EFED&\3c&H75EFED&\blur20\1a&HE0&\3a&HC0&\pos(320,18)}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:51.06,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1350,0)\1a&HFF&\3c&HC5E3EC&\pos(320,18)}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:56.05,Show_Title,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(675,0)\3c&H1EDDF0&\pos(320,18)\c&H292619&}JUJUTSU KAISEN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:03.05,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnArial\bord0\shad0\b1\pos(320,20)}December 7th, 1989
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:13.82,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fnArial\bord0\shad0\b1\pos(320,20)}Satoru Gojo Is Born
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:20.24,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:26.34,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Your present is seeing me in my uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:28.24,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:31.59,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I went with Mori High after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.95,Main,Papa,0000,0000,0000,,That's all well and good,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:36.24,Main,Papa,0000,0000,0000,,but if you do this with that much confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:38.55,Main,Papa,0000,0000,0000,,you'll turn out just like your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:42.50,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Do you hate Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:44.88,Main,Papa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hate her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.88,Main,Papa,0000,0000,0000,,but she did cheat on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.48,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.23,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:11:59.80,Main,Papa,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.69,Main,Papa,0000,0000,0000,,Honoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:07.88,Main,Papa,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:09.33,Main,Ogami,0000,0000,0000,,I killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:12.49,Main,Ogami,0000,0000,0000,,I need a corpse in order to transform \Ninto someone I've called.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:22.25,Main,Ogami,0000,0000,0000,,It was her mother that she \Nscreamed for when she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:25.60,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:28.52,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:31.71,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.78,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,It ripped halfway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.78,0:12:37.85,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.28,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:43.59,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:53.55,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,My job is killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:58.43,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,So I need to really understand \Nhow the human body works.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:02.49,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,We were
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:05.04,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:08.82,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,The sorcerers had their hands \Nfull with the cursed spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.82,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,that had grown more active over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:12.24,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we did things right,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.18,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,we could easily earn a living \Nwithout being tied down by anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:19.62,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,We curse users were free to \Nlive and do as we pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:24.94,Flashback,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Gojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:26.03,Flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:29.62,Flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The child born to the Gojo \Nclan with the Six Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.96,Flashback,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,A kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:35.45,Flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The total bounty on his head is already \Nover a hundred million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:39.11,Flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and this isn't a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:42.82,Flashback,Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's first come first served.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:52.88,Flashback,Waiter,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:35.74,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Cursed spirits had been growing \Nstronger over the years...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:39.27,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,And in that instant, \NI understood exactly why!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.53,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Because of him! Satoru Gojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:47.60,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same as when an insurmountable \Ntrack and field record was suddenly broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:50.18,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,The same as when figure \Nskaters all started adding
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:53.03,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,more revolutions to their \Njumps due to one athlete!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:57.70,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,The balance of the world changed \Nwhen Satoru Gojo was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:14:59.79,Flashback,Gojo,0000,0000,0000,,Quit looking at me, weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:03.95,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,We were free.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:08.80,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,And in our later years, \Nthat freedom was stolen from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.64,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Screw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:19.23,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never retire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:27.95,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll trample over the weak until the day I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.95,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:43.42,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what is with this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:46.04,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even about him \Nbeing tough at this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:50.06,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost certainly the \Nresult of his technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:52.71,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Is it damage nullification?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:54.05,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:58.56,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:00.78,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru Gojo is here in Shibuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:03.82,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you leave those foundations for \Nthe veil behind and get out while you can?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:07.45,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,What a lousy bluff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.12,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,"Gojo has been sealed."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:13.57,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,You were the ones shouting that so loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:17.04,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're out here having fun, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:20.08,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,If Gojo was still active, \Nwe'd be sleeping at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.04,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:24.52,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,He can't beat Gojo-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:27.08,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Fushiguro, you suck at lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:31.72,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,So this guy's technique can't be \Nsomething as grand as nullification.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.60,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,But that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:34.84,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:36.09,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:41.85,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to fight, \Nthen I'll kill you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.16,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.32,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Fleeing Hares.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:05.48,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:09.44,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured out his technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:17.64,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Transformation through Seance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.88,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,That hag is a medium?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:22.64,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not the problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.28,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.97,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Is he some famous sorcerer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.97,0:17:28.16,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell by his stance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:29.90,Italics,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,He's hella strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.32,Main,Ino,0000,0000,0000,,Number 4, Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:57.67,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,The type of shikigami \Nthat distracts with numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:18:02.52,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,So they're planning to launch a big attack \Nfrom the cover of these hares, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:06.75,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.03,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,They ran away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.04,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Max Elephant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.41,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:28.69,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Appearing and disappearing... \NTalk about restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:31.13,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a man, be clear and decisive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:34.59,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,That stuff's not my role.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:35.84,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:47.43,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,What is with this brat's power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:49.42,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,He's giving me chills!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.03,Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,For now, just keep attacking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.44,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's engine is getting revved up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.28,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.54,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,A finishing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:15.55,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,My technique is Inverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:17.37,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,While activated,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:19.98,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,attacks that hit me are made \Nweaker the stronger they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:22.30,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,and the weaker they are, \Nthe stronger they become.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:28.28,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Not one person has ever managed to dodge my \Ncounter after landing their finishing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:33.31,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,The more serious you two get, \Nthe less chance you have against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:46.28,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured out his technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:49.79,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably Inverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:54.25,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,The attack I threw out of sync \Nlanded more effectively than your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:57.02,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Fleeing Hares isn't meant for offense,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:59.80,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,but he didn't try to immediately \Nbreak through once he was surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:04.68,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's also how he managed to stay \Nperfectly fine after slamming into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:07.82,Flashback,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,So we can defeat him with a forehead flick?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:10.44,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,No, the attack can't be too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.20,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,If were just a pure inversion of force,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:16.35,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,activating it would kill himself \Nwith the minor force of air resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.02,Sign_Basic,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(175,250)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\bord1\pos(77.333,82)}True.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:19.63,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Since that doesn't happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:22.45,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,there must be an upper and \Na lower limit to his inversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:24.40,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Even with it activated,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:27.62,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,he was still matching our attacks and \Nusing cursed energy to defend from slashes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.62,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,and the effects of our techniques, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.08,Flashback,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:35.02,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,That also explains why he can't beat \Nan anomaly like Gojo-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:38.08,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,and his technique's probably a bad \Nmatch against complex techniques, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:40.98,Flashback,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we need to strike together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:45.70,Flashback,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hit him with a powerful attack and a \Nsomewhat weak attack at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.27,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:50.36,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't want him to realize \Nwe've figured out his technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:55.11,Flashback,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll keep going at full power \Nand make a show of our crazy strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:03.39,Flashback_Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start with a weak blow from Gama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:06.80,Flashback_Italics,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,Then we pummel him with a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:15.31,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,When...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.48,0:21:19.12,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,did they figure it out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:25.76,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:32.79,Main,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky over that, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:56.18,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,He stopped it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:22:00.67,Italics,Awasaka,0000,0000,0000,,He killed his momentum for just a moment—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:08.52,Main,Fushiguro,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprisingly adept.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.52,0:22:10.01,Main,Yuji,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:44.48,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you hear that the Gojos' \Nlittle Satoru-kun was sealed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:45.29,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.29,0:23:46.18,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, not interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.18,0:23:47.07,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:48.98,Main,Jogo,0000,0000,0000,,We heard this gossip from Geto-san there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.98,0:23:51.29,Main,Mahito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, heavens me! How could I? \NPlease do forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.29,0:23:52.60,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Blunt Knife."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:55.03,Next_Ep_Title,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord2\blur4}Next Episode\N{\fs30\fscy150}Blunt Knife
Dialogue: 1,0:23:52.60,0:23:54.72,Main,Geto,0000,0000,0000,,Watch in a well-lit room from a safe distance.

